{
  "page": "Wedding of Petyr Baelish and Lysa Arryn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Lysa_Arryn_AFFC.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0d/Lysa_Arryn_AFFC.jpg/300px-Lysa_Arryn_AFFC.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"213\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/0/0d/Lysa_Arryn_AFFC.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Lysa_Arryn_AFFC.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa Arryn</a>, by Lindsa Tso © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>wedding of Petyr Baelish and Lysa Arryn</b> takes place in <a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a> amid the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a> marries the widowed Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa Arryn</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Drearfort\" title=\"Drearfort\">his tower</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Fingers\" title=\"Fingers\">Fingers</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Wedding\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Wedding</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Attendees\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Attendees</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Petyr_Baelish_and_Lysa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Baelish%27s_tower.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/97/Baelish%27s_tower.jpg/250px-Baelish%27s_tower.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"326\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/97/Baelish%27s_tower.jpg/375px-Baelish%27s_tower.jpg 1.5x, /images/9/97/Baelish%27s_tower.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Baelish%27s_tower.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The <a href=\"/index.php/Drearfort\" title=\"Drearfort\">unnamed tower</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baelish\" title=\"House Baelish\">House Baelish</a>, by PHATandy ©</div></div></div>\n<p>Wounded after dueling <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark\" title=\"Brandon Stark\">Brandon Stark</a> for the hand of <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Tully</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a> impregnated Catelyn's younger sister <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa</a> while she helped him to recover. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a> forced Lysa to take <a href=\"/index.php/Tansy_tea\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tansy tea\">tansy tea</a> to abort the child,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and he arranged for her to <a href=\"/index.php/Weddings_of_Catelyn_and_Lysa_Tully\" title=\"Weddings of Catelyn and Lysa Tully\">wed</a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Arryn\" title=\"Jon Arryn\">Jon Arryn</a> during <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Under Lysa's recommendations, Jon first gave customs appointments to Petyr at the port of <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and later at <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> According to a semi-canon source, Petyr and Lysa began a secret affair.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafpetyr_baelish.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafpetyr_baelish.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaflysa_arryn.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaflysa_arryn.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When Lysa learns that Jon planned to send their son, <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Arryn\" title=\"Robert Arryn\">Robert Arryn</a>, away to be fostered at <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> with Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>, Petyr provides her with <a href=\"/index.php/Tears_of_Lys\" title=\"Tears of Lys\">poison</a> she uses to murder her husband.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The widowed Lysa is pursued by many suitors at the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>, Petyr, now <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_coin\" title=\"Master of coin\">master of coin</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"Lord of Harrenhal\">Lord of Harrenhal</a>, offers to marry Lysa and thereby bring the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a> to the side of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Petyr and Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Olenna_Tyrell\" title=\"Olenna Tyrell\">Olenna Tyrell</a> conspire to have King <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey I Baratheon</a> choke to death at his <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_Wedding\" title=\"Purple Wedding\">royal wedding</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Petyr also arranges for <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a>, daughter of his childhood infatuation Catelyn, to escape the <a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">crownlands</a> with him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> Petyr and Sansa sail on the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Merling_King\" title=\"Merling King\">Merling King</a></i> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Fingers\" title=\"Fingers\">Fingers</a>, where they wait for Lysa's arrival at Petyr's <a href=\"/index.php/Drearfort\" title=\"Drearfort\">unnamed tower</a>. To protect Sansa's identity, Petyr claims her to be his <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> daughter, \"Alayne Stone\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Wedding\">Wedding</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Petyr_Baelish_and_Lysa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Wedding\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Eight days later, Lysa arrives at the Fingers from the Eyrie with a small retinue of three maids, a dozen <a href=\"/index.php/Household_knight\" title=\"Household knight\">household knights</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">septon</a>, and the singer <a href=\"/index.php/Marillion\" title=\"Marillion\">Marillion</a>. Petyr expects for them to wed at the Eyrie with her whole court in attendance, but Lysa insists they marry that day at the Fingers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Petyr and Lysa saw their vows beneath a sky-blue canopy at sunset, and a feast is held at trestle tables beneath the Petyr's tower. They enjoy quail, venison, and roast <a href=\"/index.php/Boar\" title=\"Boar\">boar</a>, as well as a fine light <a href=\"/index.php/Mead\" title=\"Mead\">mead</a> brought by Lysa's retinue. Marillion performs \"<a href=\"/index.php/The_Vow_Unspoken\" title=\"The Vow Unspoken\">The Vow Unspoken</a>\", \"<a href=\"/index.php/Seasons_of_My_Love\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Seasons of My Love\">Seasons of My Love</a>\", and \"<a href=\"/index.php/Two_Hearts_That_Beat_as_One\" title=\"Two Hearts That Beat as One\">Two Hearts That Beat as One</a>\". The newlyweds dance to music, and several young knights dance with \"Alayne\" as well.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The knights carry Lysa up the tower for the bedding <a href=\"/index.php/Custom\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Custom\">custom</a>, and Lysa's three ladies have \"Alayne\" aid them with Petyr. Sansa can hear the married couple as they have sex upstairs, with Lysa's screams being louder than Marillion's performance of \"<a href=\"/index.php/Milady%27s_Supper\" title=\"Milady&#39;s Supper\">Milady's Supper</a>\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Sansa goes outside for a time, and the hall is dark when she returns. Several men have passed out from drinking, and another is sick in the privy. Sansa sees one of Lysa's maids kissing a knight. While Sansa scratches an <a href=\"/index.php/Old_blind_dog\" title=\"Old blind dog\">old blind dog</a> beneath the steps, a drunken Marillion tries to seduce the frightened girl. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lothor_Brune\" title=\"Lothor Brune\">Lothor Brune</a>, tasked by Petyr with protecting Sansa, interrupts and sends the singer away. Sansa has nightmares of her late brother <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb</a> dying in the same manner as Joffrey and of <a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a> replacing <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> on <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Tyrion_Lannister_and_Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Wedding of Tyrion Lannister and Sansa Stark\">her own wedding night</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The next morning, Sansa learns that Petyr has revealed her identity to Lysa, and that they intend to leave for the Eyrie that afternoon. Lysa tells Sansa that she plans to secretly marry her niece to her son, young Lord Robert Arryn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Petyr_Baelish_and_Lysa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Sardag_littlefinger.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1c/Sardag_littlefinger.jpg/250px-Sardag_littlefinger.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"391\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1c/Sardag_littlefinger.jpg/375px-Sardag_littlefinger.jpg 1.5x, /images/1/1c/Sardag_littlefinger.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Sardag_littlefinger.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a> by Sardag ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The travelers visit the <a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a> during the journey to the Eyrie,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> and Sansa meets Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Nestor_Royce\" title=\"Nestor Royce\">Nestor Royce</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/Bannermen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bannermen\">bannermen</a> of the Vale resent Lysa's marriage and that she has named Petyr as <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Protector_of_the_Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lord Protector of the Vale\">Lord Protector of the Vale</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>While helping Sansa build a snow castle of her family's ancestral home, <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, Petyr kisses the girl in the <a href=\"/index.php/Godswood_of_the_Eyrie\" title=\"Godswood of the Eyrie\">godswood of the Eyrie</a>. A jealous Lysa accuses Sansa of initiating the encounter, however, and threatens her niece by the <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Door\" title=\"Moon Door\">Moon Door</a>. Petyr temporarily soothes Lysa, assuring her that he has only ever loved one woman. He then adds \"only Cat\" and shoves Lysa out the Moon Door to her death. The killing is then blamed on the singer Marillion.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Attendees\">Attendees</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Petyr_Baelish_and_Lysa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Attendees\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baelish\" title=\"House Baelish\"><img alt=\"House Baelish of Harrenhal.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6a/House_Baelish_of_Harrenhal.svg/20px-House_Baelish_of_Harrenhal.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6a/House_Baelish_of_Harrenhal.svg/30px-House_Baelish_of_Harrenhal.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6a/House_Baelish_of_Harrenhal.svg/40px-House_Baelish_of_Harrenhal.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/20px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/30px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/40px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa Arryn</a></li>\n<li>Alayne Stone (disguised <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lothor_Brune\" title=\"Lothor Brune\"><img alt=\"Lothor Brune.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a8/Lothor_Brune.svg/20px-Lothor_Brune.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a8/Lothor_Brune.svg/30px-Lothor_Brune.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a8/Lothor_Brune.svg/40px-Lothor_Brune.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lothor_Brune\" title=\"Lothor Brune\">Lothor Brune</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Kettleblack\" title=\"House Kettleblack\"><img alt=\"House Kettleblack.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/38/House_Kettleblack.svg/20px-House_Kettleblack.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/38/House_Kettleblack.svg/30px-House_Kettleblack.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/38/House_Kettleblack.svg/40px-House_Kettleblack.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Oswell_Kettleblack\" title=\"Oswell Kettleblack\">Oswell Kettleblack</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bryen\" title=\"Bryen\">Bryen</a>\n<ul><li>Bryen's <a href=\"/index.php/Old_blind_dog\" title=\"Old blind dog\">old blind dog</a></li></ul></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grisel\" title=\"Grisel\">Grisel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kella\" title=\"Kella\">Kella</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Umfred\" title=\"Umfred\">Umfred</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Marillion\" title=\"Marillion\">Marillion</a></li>\n<li>three maids</li>\n<li>a dozen <a href=\"/index.php/Household_knight\" title=\"Household knight\">household knights</a></li>\n<li>a <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">septon</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Petyr_Baelish_and_Lysa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Marillion.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/23/Marillion.jpg/250px-Marillion.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/23/Marillion.jpg/375px-Marillion.jpg 1.5x, /images/2/23/Marillion.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Marillion.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Marillion\" title=\"Marillion\">Marillion</a> by kanako91 ©</div></div></div>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Petyr</b>: My lords, with your leave, I propose to travel to the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale</a> and there woo and win Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa Arryn</a>. Once I am her consort, I shall deliver you the Vale of Arryn without a drop of blood being spilled.<br />\n</p><p><b>Mathis</b>: Would Lady Lysa have you?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Petyr</b>: She's had me a few times before, Lord Mathis, and voiced no complaints.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Mathis_Rowan\" title=\"Mathis Rowan\">Mathis Rowan</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Lysa</b>: I want to share your bed tonight, my sweet. I want us to make another child, a brother for <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Arryn\" title=\"Robert Arryn\">Robert</a> or a sweet little daughter.<br />\n</p><p><b>Petyr</b>: I dream of that as well, sweetling. Yet there is much to be gained from a great public wedding, with all the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale</a>—<br />\n</p>\n<b>Lysa</b>: No. I want you now, this very night. And I must warn you, after all these years of silence and whisperings, I mean to scream when you love me. I am going to scream so loud they'll hear me in the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>!<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa Arryn</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Mead\" title=\"Mead\">Mead</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Marriage\" title=\"Marriage\">marriage</a> had taken years off Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa</a>. She laughed at everything so long as she held <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">her husband's</a> hand, and her eyes seemed to glow whenever she looked at him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>All night I have been making songs for you in my head. A lay for your eyes, a ballad for your lips, a duet to your breasts. I will not sing them, though. They were poor things, unworthy of such beauty. Let me sing to you with my body instead.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Marillion\" title=\"Marillion\">Marillion</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Alayne Stone</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Petyr_Baelish_and_Lysa_Arryn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.00</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.01</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.02</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.03</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.04</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.05</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.06</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref